tests.title: Lists all public repositories for the specified user.
tests.fullTitle: Github Developer API GET /users/:username/repos Lists all public repositories for the specified user.
tests.code:
this.timeout(10000);
chai.request('https://api.github.com')
.get('/users/octocat/repos')
.then((res) => {
res.should.have.status(200);
res.body.should.be.a('array');
done();
})
.catch((err) => {
throw err;
})
;

tests.code:
let stub = sinon.stub(schedule); // goes through every method on this object and replaces with a stub function
student.dropClass(1, stub.dropClass);

stub.dropClass.called.should.be.true; // stubs don't call the inner implementation of the stubbed method'
